{"tid":2012204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：山上連線 《蘋果》攝記獲獎 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-05-11T13:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T13:56:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecda44261a558cd31e798301cb7e94ccdcc04f01","tid":2012204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200511/DKVI2ZWD335MZFQIO6DVQQRJA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200511%2FDKVI2ZWD335MZFQIO6DVQQRJA4%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=fe617392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200511%2FDKVI2ZWD335MZFQIO6DVQQRJA4%2F&h=006722ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200511/DKVI2ZWD335MZFQIO6DVQQRJA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：山上連線 《蘋果》攝記獲獎 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200511/large/1589128201_0187.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200511%2Flarge%2F1589128201_0187.gif&h=ce81ebab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由香港攝影記者協會舉辦嘅《前線&middot;焦點2019》周年新聞攝影比賽噚日揭盅，《蘋果日報》攝影記者易仰民舊年中秋節喺太平山頂採訪「香港之路」特別版，拍攝咗大批市民係山頂高舉小天燈、手機電筒同雷射筆，與彼岸獅子山頂嘅市民連成一線，表達爭取五大訴求，缺一不可嘅決心，易仰民更憑着呢張獲得特寫組嘅優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n今屆比賽收到98名參賽者、合共1,117張照片同46輯圖輯，唔少得獎作品同反送中運動有關。本年度新聞年度圖片殊榮由《報導者》嘅陳朗熹奪得。八方喺呢度恭喜得獎同事同各行家，相信佢哋會繼續用相片記錄歷史，捍衞香港新聞自由。"},{"pid":"0e59dc87454220ef4023b837f5a611ad550cf34e","tid":2012204,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5c4d3f5df854768933f47ce38255fa516c87af","tid":2012204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}